    description: `Enforce access restrictions using ; and Automatically generate audit records of the enforcement actions.`,
    implementation_guidance: `Organizations log system accesses associated with applying configuration changes to ensure that configuration change control is implemented and to support after-the-fact actions should organizations discover any unauthorized changes.`,
