    title: `Continuous Guards`,
    description: `Employ guards to control to the facility where the system resides 24 hours per day, 7 days per week.`,
    implementation_guidance: `Employing guards at selected physical access points to the facility provides a more rapid response capability for organizations. Guards also provide the opportunity for human surveillance in areas of the facility not covered by video surveillance.`,
