    title: `Cryptographic Binding`,
    description: `Implement to bind security and privacy attributes to transmitted information.`,
    implementation_guidance: `Cryptographic mechanisms and techniques can provide strong security and privacy attribute binding to transmitted information to help ensure the integrity of such information.`,
